cl-contracts - Smart Contract Lifecycle Management for Common Lisp
===================================================================

This software was originally developed as part of the CLPIC project
(Common Lisp P2P Intellectual Property Chain) and has been extracted
as a standalone library.

Extracted modules:
  - src/contracts/deployment/
  - src/contracts/storage/
  - src/contracts/abi/
  - src/contracts/verification/

Authors and Contributors:
  - CLPIC Contributors

Standards Compliance:
  - Ethereum Yellow Paper (storage model)
  - EIP-1014: Skinny CREATE2
  - EIP-1153: Transient storage opcodes
  - EIP-1167: Minimal Proxy Contract
  - EIP-1967: Standard Proxy Storage Slots
  - EIP-2535: Diamond Standard
  - EIP-2929: Gas cost increases for state access
  - EIP-3860: Limit and Meter Initcode
  - ERC-1822: UUPS Proxy Standard
  - Ethereum ABI Specification
  - EIP-712: Typed structured data hashing
  - EIP-838: Error handling with custom errors

